    WEB_APP -- "WebSocket Communication" <--> AGENT_ONE & AGENT_TWO & AGENT_N

    AGENT_ONE & AGENT_TWO & AGENT_N -- "Installs on: Any OS/Server/PC" --> HOST_ENV